      <title>Revolut 将凭借新牌照开展英国和欧盟股票交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/revolut-to-launch-uk-eu-stock-trading-with-new-license</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着服务英国投资者的零售经纪商之间的竞争愈演愈烈，欧洲最有价值的金融科技公司 Revolut Ltd. 将从明年开始提供英国和欧盟上市股票的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/revolut-to-launch-uk-eu-stock-trading-with-new-license</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
